components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Invalid and required states are exposed to assistive technologies when you use `isInvalid`, `errorMessage`, and `isRequired`."},"376":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-30","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Set &#x2A;*`isWheelDisabled`** if the value should not change when the user scrolls with a pointer wheel while the field is focused."},"377":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-31","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Pair &#x2A;*`isInvalid`*&#x2A; with &#x2A;*`errorMessage`** so users get both visual and programmatic feedback."},"378":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-32","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Remember valid steps start from &#x2A;*`minValue`**."},"379":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-33","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Use &#x2A;*`isDisabled`*&#x2A; when the value cannot be changed; use &#x2A;*`isReadOnly`** when the value should be visible but not editable. Do not use them interchangeably."},"380":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-34","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"For currency or units, ensure &#x2A;*`formatOptions`** (and locale) match what users are allowed to type."},"381":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","page_id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","type":"page","content":"MetricsLockup","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup"},"382":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup-0","page_id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/