res `title` to be set — the info icon is contextually tied to the title label. If `title` is absent, `titleInfo` has no effect."},"409":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup-27","page_id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup#best-practices","content":"`trend` is intended to accompany `description` to provide temporal context (e.g. \"↑ +3% vs. last month\"). A trend icon alone, with no description, leaves the direction unanchored (\"up since *when*?\"). If `description` is not provided, `trend` has no effect."},"410":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"page","content":"Pagination","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination"},"411":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-0","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/pagination","content":"A pagination component with prev/next buttons and dot indicators, configurable page limits, and optional visibility of controls and dots"},"412":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-1","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#installation","content":"Installation"},"413":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-2","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#props","content":"Props"},"414":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-3","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#examples","content":"Examples"},"415":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-4","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#basic-usage","content":"Basic Usage"},"416":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-5","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#controlled","content":"Controlled"},"417":{"id":"/docs/compon